org.mobicents.slee.runtime.activity
Class ActivityEventQueueManagerImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.mobicents.slee.runtime.activity.ActivityEventQueueManagerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActivityEventQueueManager
public class ActivityEventQueueManagerImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ActivityEventQueueManager

Manages the queuing of events for a specific activity. Note that this impl of ActivityEventQueueManager is only thread safe if the local AC executive service is single thread.

Author:
Eduardo Martins
